Package com.oym.indoor.routing

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    IndoorRouting.GetAreaCallback
    Callback to retrieve areas from server.
    IndoorRouting.GetNotificationsCallback
    Callback to retrieve the notifications from server.
    Routing.RoutingCallback
    Callback to handle the Routing object initialization.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Area
    This class includes all the information regarding the Area Items stored in Links.
    IndoorRouting
    This class includes all the interface with the server, its calls and its callbacks.
    Instruction
    This class defines an instruction to be used in the routing
    InstructionAdapter
    This class is a helper to process the Instruction objects and retrieve the default messages and images.
    Route
    This class includes the resulting route.
    RoutePoint
    This class defines a point that shall be used for the routing.
    RouteProjectedPoint
    This class defines a projected point that shall be used for the routing.
    Routing
    This class handles all the Routing algorithm and route creation.
    RoutingResult
    This class gives the user useful information when the routing module is used.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Instruction.InstructionType
    Enumeration containing all the instructions
